{"tid":433963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"帶男人返酒店開房 內地人妻被偷手袋","createTime":"2017-10-13T00:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T15:49:18.000Z","uid":122,"like":118,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"fd47cfa6a3b21754214dff6716dcbcd18feee437","tid":433963,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:13:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>帶男人返酒店開房 內地人妻被偷手袋</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-10-13 03:55:36 HKT<br />\n<br />\n上環文咸東街138號富薈上環酒店，凌晨3時許揭發偷竊案。一名30歲姓黃內地女子，在蘭桂坊酒吧消遣時，結識一名男子，雙方瞬間打得火熱，內地女帶同該男子返酒店幽會。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，女子先到浴室沖涼，出來發現男子不知所終，手袋亦被人偷走，損失1,000元現金，她試圖追趕不慎跌倒，腳部受時，其後自行往瑪麗醫院求醫。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑她沒有錢支付費用，稍後返回酒店，並致電在深圳的丈夫求救，丈夫立即趕來香港，知道她被偷手袋，以及腳傷及發燒，於是報警。警方到場調查，酒店房間並非夫婦登記。內地女腳部骨折，需要留醫。警方將案列偷竊處理，翻查酒店閉路電視，追緝涉案30至35歲中國籍男子下落。"},{"pid":"c317930c63daee9d9a79be09b3a4d2b020f8cec5","tid":433963,"uid":41961,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a97d630a0023a9fc8f70cb2156f4f8e3d7654a","tid":433963,"uid":62060,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個老公唔知咩心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554fb35f5341334d5c0a7d79992cfe00c67afd3c","tid":433963,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b9af823f4f41df5386eeb549e5449ac8d0ebca","tid":433963,"uid":113465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"幽會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb79e44dc4a1ab0f80fe749c00e7a8002bdce225","tid":433963,"uid":29201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r